body:
The while loop in `fillOutLines` of [static/jquery-linedtextarea.js](https://play.golang.org/static/jquery-linedtextarea.js) is
causing [an infinite loop in Edge and Firefox browsers](https://github.com/hakimel/reveal.js/issues/1546)

The snippet is:
```js
/*
 * Helper function to make sure the line numbers are always kept up to
 * the current system
 */
var fillOutLines = function(linesDiv, h, lineNo) {
  while (linesDiv.height() <= h) {
    linesDiv.append("<div>" + lineNo + "</div>");
    lineNo++;
  }
  return lineNo;
};
```
